                      #    =110: volc and clim trops aerosol for lw only                   !
                      #    =111: volc and clim trops aerosol for both sw and lw            !
                      #    =  2: gocart/BSC-Dust tropspheric aerosol for sw only           !
                      #    = 20: gocart/BSC-Dust tropspheric aerosol for lw only           !
